Text.string: You! Me! Fight to the death!
Gonna turn you into a toaster!
Let the lead fly, soldier girl!
Where'd you learn how to drive?
Ain't playin' gunner for a damn Vault Thief!
Well, I guess this is yours now!
Get it off! GET IT OFF!
Put away that shield away, ya coward!
Stop hiding behind your shield, poser!
Yeah, you're cool! I get it!
Fear boner! I have a fear boner!
Where'd that bucket of bolts go?!
Not the rakks! NOT THE RAKKS!
Craaap! Watch out for that mech!
Oh, nooo! Oh no no no no!
Double the dudes, double the murder!
Your garbage tech can't fool me!
Double the geezers, double the fun!
Whatever, I'll murder all of you!
Oh god, not the arm thing!
Let me go! Let me gooo!
Look at the size of that thing!
Aw, man! We had a suicide pact!
You can't kill all of us!
See you in the Great Vault!
Another sacrifice for the Twin Gods!
Stay down! Also stop breathing! Wait, write me into your will first!
You'll remember my name! Which is-- [death rattle]
Tell my kids... I wish they were born...
My chili recipe dies with me!
With my last breath, I curse Claptrap!
We are the CHILDREN OF THE VAULT!
Aw, stop runnin', you'll ruin the meat!
You're gonna be meat when I'm done!
You should give up, Vault Thief!
Ha! I'm crazier than you'll ever be!
Don't get between me and my gun, heretic!
You think you can get past me, huh?
Come on, fam! Let's freakin' DO THIS!
Let's wreck these guys! Come on, EVERYONE!
Who's pumped? I'm pumped! You guys pumped?!
Just a sec -- I gotta celebrate!
You WATCH this time. Watch me!
Yeahhh! That's what you get when you mess with us!
Never shoulda tried to take us on!
That's right! I'm the one who got you!
Take a good look, Vault Thief!
All right! Another Vault Thief gets it, woo!
Victory! That's right, callin' it right here!
Suck it! Chalk another one up for the COV!
You ain't got a chance, Vault Thief!
I'll show you the power of the Twin Gods!
Let's get a little more intimate!
I'll blast you in a second!
Need some more boom in my life!
Just -- hold on a minute, will ya?!
Just you wait. Just you wait!
Hope there's enough left to cook!
You'll look better with bullet holes!
Takin' down Vault Thieves! Hell yeah!
I'll die here if I have to!
Come at me, scrublord! I'm ripped!
This is where we hold them!
Where do you think you're goin'?!
You can't take all of us! Right?
This wasn't part of the plan!
